# to be [[aware]] of (something), to be aware that …, to know that …
#: {{syn|fr|[[être]] [[conscient]] [[de]]/[[que]]}}

====Usage notes====
* Followed by a substantive introduced by the preposition {{m|fr|de}} (''avoir conscience de quelque chose''), or by a [[subordinate clause]] introduced by the conjunction {{m|fr|que}} (''avoir conscience que …'').

====See also====
* {{l|fr|avoir connaissance}}
* {{l|fr|avoir bonne conscience}}
